## <a id="reqs"></a>Requirements

Zettaset XCrypt Full Disk has the following requirements:

+ java 1.7.0 or greater

+ Java Cryptography Extension (JCE) Unlimited Strength Juridiction Policy files

+ libselinux-python and cryptsetup-luks

+ wget

+ nss version 3.21 or greater

+ xfsprogs and xfsdump, when using the xfs file system

+ Zettaset Virtual Enterprise Key Manager (V-EKM). To download V-EKM, contact our [sales team](mailto:sales@zettaset.com).


